  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220&deg;C/ 200&deg;C (fan)/ 425&deg;F/ Gas 7</p>\r\n<p>Top, tail and chop the&nbsp;<strong>courgette<span class=\"text-danger\">[s] </span></strong>into bite-sized chunks</p>\r\n<p>Deseed the <strong>yellow</strong>&nbsp;<strong>pepper<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into thin strips</p>\r\n<p>Peel and finely slice the <strong>red onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s] </span></strong></p>\r\n<p>Peel and finely slice (don't chop!) the&nbsp;<strong>garlic</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1445.-step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1445.-step-1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1445.-step-1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1445.-step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1445.-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a matching lid with a drizzle of&nbsp;<strong>olive oil</strong> over a high heat</p>\r\n<p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced red onion</strong> and <strong>yellow&nbsp;pepper</strong> with a pinch of<strong> salt&nbsp;</strong>and cook for 5-8 min or until softened</p>\r\n<p>Once softened, add the <strong>courgette chunks</strong> and <strong>garlic slices</strong> and cook for a further 5 min until beginning to brown</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1445.-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1445.-step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1445.-step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1445.-step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1445.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, boil a kettle</p>\r\n<p>Dissolve the <strong>vegetable stock cube<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong><span class=\"text-danger\">&nbsp;</span>in 450ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[850ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p>\r\n<p>Once the <strong>vegetables</strong>&nbsp;have softened, add the <strong>dried&nbsp;oregano</strong> and<strong> tomato paste</strong>&nbsp;and cook for 1 min</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1445.-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1445.-step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1445.-step-3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1445.-step-3-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1445.-step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the&nbsp;<strong>vegetable stock </strong>and&nbsp;<strong>balsamic vinegar&nbsp;</strong>to the pan and reduce the heat to medium-low</p>\r\n<p>Cook for 10-15 min or until the sauce has thickened slightly and the liquid has reduced by half&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
